var book = {
	"name": "Colossians",
	"numChapters": 4,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29467A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29467A\"></sup>Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29467B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29467B\"></sup>an apostle of Jesus Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29467C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29467C\"></sup>by the will of God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29467D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29467D\"></sup>Timothy our brother,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29468E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29468E\"></sup>saints and faithful brethren in Christ <i>who are</i> at Colossae: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29468F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29468F\"></sup>Grace to you and peace from God our Father.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29469G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29469G\"></sup>We give thanks to God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29469H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29469H\"></sup>the Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, praying always for you,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29470I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29470I\"></sup>since we heard of your faith in Christ Jesus and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29470J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29470J\"></sup>love which you have for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29470K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29470K\"></sup>all the saints;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29471L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29471L\"></sup>hope <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29471M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29471M\"></sup>laid up for you in heaven, of which you previously <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29471N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29471N\"></sup>heard in the word of truth, the gospel",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>which has come to you, just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29472O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29472O\"></sup>in all the world also it is constantly bearing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29472P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29472P\"></sup>fruit and increasing, even as <i>it has been doing</i> in you also since the day you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29472Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29472Q\"></sup>heard <i>of it</i> and understood the grace of God in truth;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>just as you learned <i>it</i> from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29473R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29473R\"></sup>Epaphras, our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29473S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29473S\"></sup>beloved fellow bond-servant, who is a faithful servant of Christ on our behalf,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and he also informed us of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29474T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29474T\"></sup>love in the Spirit.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For this reason also, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29475U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29475U\"></sup>since the day we heard <i>of it</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29475V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29475V\"></sup>we have not ceased to pray for you and to ask that you may be filled with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29475W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29475W\"></sup>knowledge of His will in all spiritual <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29475X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29475X\"></sup>wisdom and understanding,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>so that you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29476Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29476Y\"></sup>walk in a manner worthy of the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29476Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29476Z\"></sup>to please <i>Him</i> in all respects, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29476AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29476AA\"></sup>bearing fruit in every good work and increasing in the knowledge of God;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29477AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29477AB\"></sup>strengthened with all power, according to His glorious might, for the attaining of all steadfastness and patience; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29477AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29477AC\"></sup>joyously",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>giving thanks to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29478AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29478AD\"></sup>the Father, who has qualified us to share in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29478AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29478AE\"></sup>the inheritance of the saints in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29478AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29478AF\"></sup>Light.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For He rescued us from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29479AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29479AG\"></sup>domain of darkness, and transferred us to the kingdom of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29479AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29479AH\"></sup>His beloved Son,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29480AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29480AI\"></sup>in whom we have redemption, the forgiveness of sins.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29481AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29481AJ\"></sup>image of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29481AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29481AK\"></sup>invisible God, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29481AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29481AL\"></sup>firstborn of all creation.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29482AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29482AM\"></sup>by Him all things were created, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29482AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29482AN\"></sup><i>both</i> in the heavens and on earth, visible and invisible, whether <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29482AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29482AO\"></sup>thrones or dominions or rulers or authorities—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29482AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29482AP\"></sup>all things have been created through Him and for Him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29483AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29483AQ\"></sup>is before all things, and in Him all things hold together.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He is also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29484AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29484AR\"></sup>head of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29484AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29484AS\"></sup>the body, the church; and He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29484AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29484AT\"></sup>the beginning, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29484AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29484AU\"></sup>the firstborn from the dead, so that He Himself will come to have first place in everything.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29485AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29485AV\"></sup>the <i>Father’s</i> good pleasure for all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29485AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29485AW\"></sup>the fullness to dwell in Him,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and through Him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29486AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29486AX\"></sup>reconcile all things to Himself, having made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29486AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29486AY\"></sup>peace through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29486AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29486AZ\"></sup>the blood of His cross; through Him, <i>I say</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29486BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29486BA\"></sup>whether things on earth or things in heaven.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And although you were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29487BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29487BB\"></sup>formerly alienated and hostile in mind, <i>engaged</i> in evil deeds,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>yet He has now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29488BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29488BC\"></sup>reconciled you in His fleshly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29488BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29488BD\"></sup>body through death, in order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29488BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29488BE\"></sup>present you before Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29488BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29488BF\"></sup>holy and blameless and beyond reproach—",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>if indeed you continue in the faith firmly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29489BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29489BG\"></sup>established and steadfast, and not moved away from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29489BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29489BH\"></sup>hope of the gospel that you have heard, which was proclaimed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29489BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29489BI\"></sup>in all creation under heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29489BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29489BJ\"></sup>and of which I, Paul, was made a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29489BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29489BK\"></sup>minister.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29490BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29490BL\"></sup>Now I rejoice in my sufferings for your sake, and in my flesh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29490BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29490BM\"></sup>I do my share on behalf of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29490BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29490BN\"></sup>His body, which is the church, in filling up what is lacking in Christ’s afflictions.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29491BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29491BO\"></sup>Of <i>this church</i> I was made a minister according to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29491BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29491BP\"></sup>stewardship from God bestowed on me for your benefit, so that I might fully carry out the <i>preaching of</i> the word of God,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><i>that is</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29492BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29492BQ\"></sup>the mystery which has been hidden from the <i>past</i> ages and generations, but has now been manifested to His saints,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>to whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29493BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29493BR\"></sup>God willed to make known what is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29493BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29493BS\"></sup>the riches of the glory of this mystery among the Gentiles, which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29493BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29493BT\"></sup>Christ in you, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29493BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29493BU\"></sup>hope of glory.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>We proclaim Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29494BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29494BV\"></sup>admonishing every man and teaching every man with all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29494BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29494BW\"></sup>wisdom, so that we may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29494BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29494BX\"></sup>present every man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29494BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29494BY\"></sup>complete in Christ.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For this purpose also I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29495BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29495BZ\"></sup>labor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29495CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29495CA\"></sup>striving <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29495CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29495CB\"></sup>according to His power, which mightily works within me."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>For I want you to know how great a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29496A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29496A\"></sup>struggle I have on your behalf and for those who are at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29496B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29496B\"></sup>Laodicea, and for all those who have not personally seen my face,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>that their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29497C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29497C\"></sup>hearts may be encouraged, having been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29497D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29497D\"></sup>knit together in love, and <i>attaining</i> to all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29497E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29497E\"></sup>the wealth that comes from the full assurance of understanding, <i>resulting</i> in a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29497F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29497F\"></sup>true knowledge of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29497G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29497G\"></sup>God’s mystery, <i>that is</i>, Christ <i>Himself</i>,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>in whom are hidden all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29498H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29498H\"></sup>the treasures of wisdom and knowledge.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29499I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29499I\"></sup>I say this so that no one will delude you with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29499J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29499J\"></sup>persuasive argument.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For even though I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29500K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29500K\"></sup>absent in body, nevertheless I am with you in spirit, rejoicing to see your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29500L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29500L\"></sup>good discipline and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29500M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29500M\"></sup>stability of your faith in Christ.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore as you have received <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29501N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29501N\"></sup>Christ Jesus the Lord, <i>so</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29501O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29501O\"></sup>walk in Him,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>having been firmly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29502P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29502P\"></sup>rooted <i>and now</i> being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29502Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29502Q\"></sup>built up in Him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29502R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29502R\"></sup>established in your faith, just as you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29502S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29502S\"></sup>were instructed, <i>and</i> overflowing with gratitude.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29503T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29503T\"></sup>See to it that no one takes you captive through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29503U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29503U\"></sup>philosophy and empty deception, according to the tradition of men, according to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29503V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29503V\"></sup>elementary principles of the world, rather than according to Christ.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For in Him all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29504W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29504W\"></sup>fullness of Deity dwells in bodily form,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and in Him you have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29505X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29505X\"></sup>made complete, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29505Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29505Y\"></sup>He is the head over all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29505Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29505Z\"></sup>rule and authority;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and in Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29506AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29506AA\"></sup>you were also circumcised with a circumcision made without hands, in the removal of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29506AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29506AB\"></sup>the body of the flesh by the circumcision of Christ;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>having been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29507AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29507AC\"></sup>buried with Him in baptism, in which you were also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29507AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29507AD\"></sup>raised up with Him through faith in the working of God, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29507AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29507AE\"></sup>raised Him from the dead.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When you were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29508AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29508AF\"></sup>dead in your transgressions and the uncircumcision of your flesh, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29508AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29508AG\"></sup>made you alive together with Him, having forgiven us all our transgressions,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>having canceled out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29509AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29509AH\"></sup>the certificate of debt consisting of decrees against us, which was hostile to us; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29509AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29509AI\"></sup>He has taken it out of the way, having nailed it to the cross.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When He had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29510AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29510AJ\"></sup>disarmed the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29510AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29510AK\"></sup>rulers and authorities, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29510AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29510AL\"></sup>made a public display of them, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29510AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29510AM\"></sup>triumphed over them through Him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore no one is to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29511AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29511AN\"></sup>act as your judge in regard to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29511AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29511AO\"></sup>food or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29511AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29511AP\"></sup>drink or in respect to a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29511AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29511AQ\"></sup>festival or a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29511AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29511AR\"></sup>new moon or a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29511AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29511AS\"></sup>Sabbath day—",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>things which are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29512AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29512AT\"></sup>a <i>mere</i> shadow of what is to come; but the substance belongs to Christ.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Let no one keep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29513AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29513AU\"></sup>defrauding you of your prize by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29513AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29513AV\"></sup>delighting in self-abasement and the worship of the angels, taking his stand on <i>visions</i> he has seen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29513AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29513AW\"></sup>inflated without cause by his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29513AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29513AX\"></sup>fleshly mind,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and not holding fast to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29514AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29514AY\"></sup>the head, from whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29514AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29514AZ\"></sup>the entire body, being supplied and held together by the joints and ligaments, grows with a growth which is from God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29515BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29515BA\"></sup>If you have died with Christ to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29515BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29515BB\"></sup>elementary principles of the world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29515BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29515BC\"></sup>why, as if you were living in the world, do you submit yourself to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29515BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29515BD\"></sup>decrees, such as,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Do not handle, do not taste, do not touch!”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>(which all <i>refer</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29517BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29517BE\"></sup><i>to</i> things destined to perish with use)—in accordance with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29517BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29517BF\"></sup>commandments and teachings of men?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>These are matters which have, to be sure, the appearance of wisdom in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29518BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29518BG\"></sup>self-made religion and self-abasement and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29518BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29518BH\"></sup>severe treatment of the body, <i>but are</i> of no value against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29518BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29518BI\"></sup>fleshly indulgence."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Therefore if you have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29519A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29519A\"></sup>raised up with Christ, keep seeking the things above, where Christ is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29519B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29519B\"></sup>seated at the right hand of God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29520C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29520C\"></sup>Set your mind on the things above, not on the things that are on earth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29521D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29521D\"></sup>died and your life is hidden with Christ in God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29522E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29522E\"></sup>who is our life, is revealed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29522F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29522F\"></sup>then you also will be revealed with Him in glory.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29523G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29523G\"></sup>Therefore consider <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29523H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29523H\"></sup>the members of your earthly body as dead to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29523I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29523I\"></sup>immorality, impurity, passion, evil desire, and greed, which amounts to idolatry.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For it is because of these things that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29524J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29524J\"></sup>the wrath of God will come upon the sons of disobedience,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29525K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29525K\"></sup>in them you also once walked, when you were living in them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But now you also, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29526L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29526L\"></sup>put them all aside: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29526M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29526M\"></sup>anger, wrath, malice, slander, <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29526N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29526N\"></sup>abusive speech from your mouth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29527O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29527O\"></sup>Do not lie to one another, since you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29527P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29527P\"></sup>laid aside the old self with its <i>evil</i> practices,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29528Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29528Q\"></sup>put on the new self who is being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29528R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29528R\"></sup>renewed to a true knowledge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29528S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29528S\"></sup>according to the image of the One who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29528T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29528T\"></sup>created him—",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><i>a renewal</i> in which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29529U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29529U\"></sup>there is no <i>distinction between</i> Greek and Jew, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29529V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29529V\"></sup>circumcised and uncircumcised, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29529W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29529W\"></sup>barbarian, Scythian, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29529X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29529X\"></sup>slave and freeman, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29529Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29529Y\"></sup>Christ is all, and in all.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So, as those who have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29530Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29530Z\"></sup>chosen of God, holy and beloved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29530AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29530AA\"></sup>put on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29530AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29530AB\"></sup>heart of compassion, kindness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29530AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29530AC\"></sup>humility, gentleness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29530AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29530AD\"></sup>patience;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29531AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29531AE\"></sup>bearing with one another, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29531AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29531AF\"></sup>forgiving each other, whoever has a complaint against anyone; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29531AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29531AG\"></sup>just as the Lord forgave you, so also should you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Beyond all these things <i>put on</i> love, which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29532AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29532AH\"></sup>the perfect bond of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29532AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29532AI\"></sup>unity.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29533AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29533AJ\"></sup>the peace of Christ rule in your hearts, to which indeed you were called in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29533AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29533AK\"></sup>one body; and be thankful.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29534AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29534AL\"></sup>the word of Christ richly dwell within you, with all wisdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29534AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29534AM\"></sup>teaching and admonishing one another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29534AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29534AN\"></sup>with psalms <i>and</i> hymns <i>and</i> spiritual songs, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29534AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29534AO\"></sup>singing with thankfulness in your hearts to God.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29535AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29535AP\"></sup>Whatever you do in word or deed, <i>do</i> all in the name of the Lord Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29535AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29535AQ\"></sup>giving thanks through Him to God the Father.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29536AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29536AR\"></sup>Wives, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29536AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29536AS\"></sup>be subject to your husbands, as is fitting in the Lord.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29537AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29537AT\"></sup>Husbands, love your wives and do not be embittered against them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29538AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29538AU\"></sup>Children, be obedient to your parents in all things, for this is well-pleasing to the Lord.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29539AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29539AV\"></sup>Fathers, do not exasperate your children, so that they will not lose heart.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29540AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29540AW\"></sup>Slaves, in all things obey those who are your masters on earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29540AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29540AX\"></sup>not with external service, as those who <i>merely</i> please men, but with sincerity of heart, fearing the Lord.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Whatever you do, do your work heartily, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29541AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29541AY\"></sup>as for the Lord rather than for men,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29542AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29542AZ\"></sup>knowing that from the Lord you will receive the reward of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29542BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29542BA\"></sup>the inheritance. It is the Lord Christ whom you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29542BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29542BB\"></sup>serve.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29543BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29543BC\"></sup>he who does wrong will receive the consequences of the wrong which he has done, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29543BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29543BD\"></sup>that without partiality."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Masters, grant to your slaves justice and fairness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29544A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29544A\"></sup>knowing that you too have a Master in heaven.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29545B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29545B\"></sup>Devote yourselves to prayer, keeping alert in it with <i>an attitude of</i> thanksgiving;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>praying at the same time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29546C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29546C\"></sup>for us as well, that God will open up to us a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29546D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29546D\"></sup>door for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29546E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29546E\"></sup>the word, so that we may speak forth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29546F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29546F\"></sup>the mystery of Christ, for which I have also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29546G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29546G\"></sup>been imprisoned;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>that I may make it clear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29547H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29547H\"></sup>in the way I ought to speak.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29548I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29548I\"></sup>Conduct yourselves with wisdom toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29548J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29548J\"></sup>outsiders, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29548K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29548K\"></sup>making the most of the opportunity.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29549L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29549L\"></sup>Let your speech always be with grace, <i>as though</i> seasoned with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29549M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29549M\"></sup>salt, so that you will know how you should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29549N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29549N\"></sup>respond to each person.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29550O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29550O\"></sup>As to all my affairs, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29550P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29550P\"></sup>Tychicus, <i>our</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29550Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29550Q\"></sup>beloved brother and faithful servant and fellow bond-servant in the Lord, will bring you information.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29551R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29551R\"></sup><i>For</i> I have sent him to you for this very purpose, that you may know about our circumstances and that he may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29551S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29551S\"></sup>encourage your hearts;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29552T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29552T\"></sup>Onesimus, <i>our</i> faithful and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29552U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29552U\"></sup>beloved brother, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29552V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29552V\"></sup>who is one of your <i>number</i>. They will inform you about the whole situation here.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29553W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29553W\"></sup>Aristarchus, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29553X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29553X\"></sup>fellow prisoner, sends you his greetings; and <i>also</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29553Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29553Y\"></sup>Barnabas’s cousin Mark (about whom you received instructions; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29553Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29553Z\"></sup>if he comes to you, welcome him);",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and <i>also</i> Jesus who is called Justus; these are the only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29554AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29554AA\"></sup>fellow workers for the kingdom of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29554AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29554AB\"></sup>who are from the circumcision, and they have proved to be an encouragement to me.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29555AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29555AC\"></sup>Epaphras, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29555AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29555AD\"></sup>who is one of your number, a bondslave of Jesus Christ, sends you his greetings, always <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29555AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29555AE\"></sup>laboring earnestly for you in his prayers, that you may stand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29555AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29555AF\"></sup>perfect and fully assured in all the will of God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For I testify for him that he has a deep concern for you and for those who are in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29556AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29556AG\"></sup>Laodicea and Hierapolis.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29557AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29557AH\"></sup>Luke, the beloved physician, sends you his greetings, and <i>also</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29557AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29557AI\"></sup>Demas.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Greet the brethren who are in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29558AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29558AJ\"></sup>Laodicea and also Nympha and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29558AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29558AK\"></sup>the church that is in her house.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29559AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29559AL\"></sup>When this letter is read among you, have it also read in the church of the Laodiceans; and you, for your part <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29559AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29559AM\"></sup>read my letter <i>that is coming</i> from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29559AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29559AN\"></sup>Laodicea.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Say to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29560AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29560AO\"></sup>Archippus, “Take heed to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29560AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29560AP\"></sup>ministry which you have received in the Lord, that you may fulfill it.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I, Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29561AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29561AQ\"></sup>write this greeting with my own hand. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29561AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29561AR\"></sup>Remember my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29561AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29561AS\"></sup>imprisonment. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29561AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29561AT\"></sup>Grace be with you."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;